Dar es Salaam. Some 7,700 Tanzanians have won a total of Sh155 million for predicting results of matches of various European leagues through M-Bet.M-Bet director Dhiresh Kaba said yesterday that through the betting platform, some participants have won Sh100,000 and others Sh2.5 million. The response of Tanzanians to participate in predicting results of various European football matches through M-Bet has been very impressive.This is also because they have realised that our betting platform is genuine since as long as one s bet is successful, we send them their money as soon as possible, he said.